    <item>
      <title>韩国金融监管机构正在调查“过热”的韩国锌矿争夺战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/korean-financial-watchdog-probing-overheated-korea-zinc-battle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着全球最大锌精炼厂的争夺愈演愈烈，韩国金融监管机构将对韩国锌业公司收购战中可能存在的不公平交易行为展开调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/korean-financial-watchdog-probing-overheated-korea-zinc-battle</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 03:52:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着休闲目的地的转变，雅高仍对中国市场“下大赌注”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/accor-still-betting-big-on-china-as-leisure-destinations-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雅高集团表示，中国游客对探索偏僻景点的兴趣日益浓厚，支撑了后疫情时代的旅游热潮，并支撑了中国黄金周假期的强劲需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/accor-still-betting-big-on-china-as-leisure-destinations-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 03:46:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡永久居民可免签证进入印度尼西亚巴淡岛和民丹岛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/singapore-prs-get-visa-free-entry-to-indonesia-s-batam-bintan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼将给予持有新加坡永久居留权的外国人免签证入境巴淡岛、民丹岛和吉里汶群岛，旨在促进这些区域经济区的旅游业和投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/singapore-prs-get-visa-free-entry-to-indonesia-s-batam-bintan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 03:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国誓言实现经济目标，不会采取大规模刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-vows-to-hit-economic-goals-stops-short-of-large-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，有信心实现今年的经济目标，并承诺进一步支持经济增长，尽管中国并未推出更多重大刺激措施，这令寻求更多动力推动全球股市上涨的投资者感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-vows-to-hit-economic-goals-stops-short-of-large-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 02:53:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于北京暂缓实施重大刺激措施，中国股市涨势降温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-stocks-surge-on-return-from-holidays-as-euphoria-extends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员质疑北京方面推出更多刺激措施的决心，一周假期过后，中国境内股市的涨势有所降温。香港股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-stocks-surge-on-return-from-holidays-as-euphoria-extends</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pictet 文件错误地显示了 150 亿美元的中国银行押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/pictet-filing-mistakenly-showed-15-billion-bet-on-chinese-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港交易所的一份文件错误地显示，百达资产管理公司向中国建设银行股份有限公司投资了 1,212 亿港元（156 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/pictet-filing-mistakenly-showed-15-billion-bet-on-chinese-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 00:40:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚央行暗示维持基准利率不变，直至对价格有信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/rba-signals-key-rate-to-stay-at-4-35-until-confident-on-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上次董事会会议记录显示，澳大利亚央行将维持利率在当前的 12 年来的最高水平，直到确信通胀率持续向目标水平靠拢，这表明政策放松仍有一段距离。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/rba-signals-key-rate-to-stay-at-4-35-until-confident-on-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市涨势减弱，亚洲股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市全球领先，但在一场预计将公布经济刺激措施的重要新闻发布会令投资者失望后，股市涨势失去动力。香港股市暴跌，日元上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 22:34:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
